---
title: Mumbai Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Garlic Yoghurt & Flaked Almonds
description: This gorgeous plate of colour doesn't just look good - it's a nutritionally balanced combo of succulent yoghurt
chicken, rainbow roasted veggies and zingy pickled onion. Flavour is just written all over it.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
